There are currently 1410 homes for sale in Seattle at a median listing price of $689K. Some of these homes are "Hot Homes," meaning they're likely to sell quickly. Most homes for sale in Seattle stay on the market for 53 days and receive 1 offers. In the past month, 745 homes have been sold in Seattle. In addition to houses in Seattle, there were also 801 condos, 555 townhouses, and 83 multi-family units for sale in Seattle last month. Seattle is a fairly walkable city in King County with a Walk Score of 73. Seattle is home to approximately 608,091 people and 507,408 jobs. Popular neighborhoods include Downtown Seattle, Queen Anne, First Hill, Leschi, Pioneer Square, University District, Belltown, Madison Valley, Lake Union, Madison Park, Madrona, Wallingford, Lower Queen Anne, Eastlake, and Mount Baker.
